ROCKY (1976) 92% Rocky Balboa vs. Apollo Creed Here the most influential and iconic bout in the history ofHollywood. Rocky's battle with Apollo Creed has been reworked in countless ways across numerous genres; it's evoked in virtually every scrappy-underdog tale. However, none have been quite able to match the original for spine- tingling tension Even its over-familiarity (it plays on Jumbotrons in sports arenas virtually every night) hasn't dulled its impact; in addition to being oreathlessy exciting and dramatically potent, it doesn't end quite the way you'd expect. M Rocky Balboa Vs Apollo Creed'.

node.text: Very proud that ROTTEN TOMATOES has chosen Rocky versus Apollo Creed as the greatest fight scene in the history of cinema!
